default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultI have little experience of the internet and of technology generall
defaulty, but I regret the declining influence of a simple godly way of life, whilst acknowledging much good has arrived with the electronic age.  I was always taught that the best way to distract a child and to save it from danger is to offer something else to d
defaultraw its attention whilst removing the danger – such as a knife – at the same time.
